-- Libya joins OPEC meeting in Vienna
-- 
-- Wed Jun 8, 2011 8:28am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/08/us-opec-libya-idUSTRE7572K420110608

 

 VIENNA  (Reuters) - Libya's OPEC envoy joined the meeting of oil ministers three hours after their closed session talks began, an OPEC official said on Wednesday. 

 Libya is represented at the meeting by Omran Abukraa, who was appointed after top oil official Shokri Ghanem defected.